# ── ROBBED_ · MAINNET (Robinhood Chain, chain id 4663) ──────────────────────
# Build-time PUBLIC env for the Cloudflare Workers frontend (robbed.fun).
# All NEXT_PUBLIC_* are inlined at `next build` (a runtime Worker var can't
# override an inlined value). No secrets here.
#
# ⚠ INTERIM TOPOLOGY (2026-07-12): the robbed.fun Worker consumes the
# mainnet-stack API at api.robbed.fun (tunnel), but that stack currently runs
# the INTERIM TESTNET env — chain 46630, real 46630 contracts ("later we
# replace testnet by mainnet"). Lines marked "# INTERIM (Phase-B swap: ...)"
# flip back to their mainnet values when the stack switches to mainnet.
# API_BASE_URL / WS_URL below already survive Phase B unchanged.
# INTERIM (Phase-B swap: NEXT_PUBLIC_CHAIN_ID=4663)
NEXT_PUBLIC_CHAIN_ID=46630
# INTERIM (Phase-B swap: NEXT_PUBLIC_RPC_HTTP=https://rpc.mainnet.chain.robinhood.com)
NEXT_PUBLIC_RPC_HTTP=https://rpc.testnet.chain.robinhood.com
# INTERIM (Phase-B swap: restore NEXT_PUBLIC_RPC_WS=wss://feed.mainnet.chain.robinhood.com)
# — deliberately UNSET for 46630: no public WS JSON-RPC on testnet (feed.* is
# the SEQUENCER FEED, not JSON-RPC — .env.testnet header rule); env.ts
# tolerates empty (viem stays on the HTTP transport).
# NEXT_PUBLIC_RPC_WS=
NEXT_PUBLIC_API_BASE_URL=https://api.robbed.fun
NEXT_PUBLIC_WS_URL=wss://api.robbed.fun/ws
NEXT_PUBLIC_R2_PUBLIC_BASE_URL=https://pub-1f7ef06884964a2f82e21cd86e1893b0.r2.dev
# NEXT_PUBLIC_WALLETCONNECT_PROJECT_ID=   # set your WalletConnect project id
# NEXT_PUBLIC_LARGE_VALUE_ETH_THRESHOLD=1.0

